    <Section>
      <h1 class="text-4xl text-skin-secondary underline decoration-4 decoration-skin-secondaryInverted md:text-5xl font-bold pb-4">ðŸ¤– About me</h1>
      <p class="pb-3">
        I'm a Software Engineer @{" "}
        <a
          class="transition underline hover:text-[#e40085] font-bold hover:font-extrabold"
          href="https://www.cancerresearchuk.org/"
        >
          Cancer Research UK
        </a>, building{" "}
        <a
          class="transition underline hover:text-[#0070f3] font-bold hover:font-extrabold"
